Folder created March 4 2026 to create Phecode-ICD mappings from PheWAS resources,
bypassing the Google Sheets mappings previously provided.

*** Descriptions of R files ***

figureThingsOut.R
---
Compare PheWAS mappings to Google Sheets mappings. With this comparison, I 
noticed that phecodes included children phecodes that map to their parents.

mapPhecodesToICDs.R +
helpers.R +
customMapPhecodesToExclusions.R
---
Read in previously provided list of mappings only to get phecodes we want for
the study. Use PheWAS package to find all child phecodes mapping to them and
associated exclusion phecodes. Then map inclusion and exclusion phecodes to 
ICD codes

*** .csv files ***

Time-to-event_Phenotype_sample_sizes - _Corrected_ Phecode_ICD_map.csv
---
Downloaded on Feb 27, 2026 from the corrected Google Sheet that was shared with 
GBMI members. One phecode per row.

phecode_definitions1.2.csv
Phecode_map_v1_2_icd9_icd10cm.csv
---
Downloaded on March 3, 2026 from https://phewascatalog.org/phewas/#phe12.

phewas1_2_mappingPlus.csv
---
Output from mapPhecodesToICDs.R
"Plus" refers to the fact that we manually added a few ICD codes (listed below) 
to the case inclusion ICDs for heart failure and COPD from the Google sheets mapping. 
Without these ICD codes, sample sizes decrease by over 1000 per phenotype.

428.2/Heart failure NOS: I50.0, I50.9
496.21/COPD: J44.8, J44.9